@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qgncrb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.11)) / (tmp + 0.05))
    v1 = (v2 + (wp.cos(v1 + 0.72) / v0))
    tmp = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.17 - v0 + 0.63) * wp.abs(v1 + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
